snippet.title: Rainbow Six Siege: Operation Shifting Tides – Wamai & Kali Trailer
snippet.description:
Operation Shifting Tides is available now!

Hold onto your seats, Operation Shifting Tides is rising from the depths. NIGHTHAVEN Special Intervention Group joins the fray as this season’s new ORG. Its owner, Kali, joins Six with one of her best agents, Wamai.
